  "content": [
    {
      "type": "TEXT",
      "value": "<p>The vec_sum(x) operator adds up every value in the vector field x and returns the total. This is useful for aggregating data points stored as vectors, such as total daily sentiment volume or total trades for a stock.</p><p><b>Example calculations</b></p>",
      "id": "26728c43-9a65-44e6-9379-41e86de9ac93"
    },
    {
