      },
      "id": "9a38c324-a6ef-499c-bbff-3351c8c5f466"
    },
    {
      "type": "TEXT",
      "value": "<p><b>Examples</b></p><p>vec_sum(scl12_alltype_buzzvec)</p><ul><li>Sums all entries of the intraday “buzz” vector to get a daily total volume of mentions for each instrument.</li></ul>",
